As a parent of a former Pretoria Boys’ High pupil, your comment in "Good Week/Bad Week" (Fox, January 14-20) about "former schoolmasters [crawling out of the woodwork]" misjudges the facts. Former Pretoria Boys’ headmaster Bill Schroder approached all current and former pupils, and all (voluntary) contributors are named on the school notice board, regardless of the amount they contributed. Elon Musk was treated the same as everyone else. Mr Schroder’s sterling reputation made a "begging bowl" unnecessary. MCPretoria The FM welcomes concise letters from readers. They can be sent to fmmail@fm.co.za